{"tid":1592170,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[好撚緊急 再開]  十月一要集中去港島既比少少耐性好唔好呀？？？","createTime":"2019-09-24T13:09:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T14:10:13.000Z","uid":56518,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"11699f69b758a1034df475c59cb93a02881f50f1","tid":1592170,"uid":56518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T13:09:56.000Z","msg":"收工行過公園，同個呀叔傾計佢叫我幫佢開post同大家講<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n10.1點解要分5/18區，而唔集中去港島既論點已經有好多巴打講左，只係有啲補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你地話想吹雞，想黎多次200萬人遊行，唔係唔得，但點樣先可以再令濕鳩政府批呀？<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要令佢地覺得驚呀！驚到佢地寧願比你港島遊行都唔想比你五區曬馬呀！好似八月五果次咁呀！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PC29BSm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPC29BSm.jpg&h=43b94066&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n依場係持久戰，講緊可能五年、十年<br />\n10.1絕對唔係end game。<br />\n<br />\n只要10.1我地氣勢最強既時候比到極大壓力依班撚屌黑警同政府，令到佢地意識到: 呀屌原來任由佢地班人咁多區周圍搞，好似比起批准佢地大遊行而付出嘅代價更加大喎，咁下次都係批左佢好過<br />\n<br />\n依個就係我地出師有名既原因！！！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">從來主權在民，唔應該係政府迫我地揀！而係我地做主動迫佢地揀！！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">時間得返幾日，快啲比個共識！！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong>"},{"pid":"3953c4dc27bc4351ea35e1f8a6bd335a4b49c4df","tid":1592170,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T13:10:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"col